snippet.title: Crooked Waters Alpha - Crewing a Pirate Ship in VR
snippet.description:
Apologies about the audio! We got to play some Crooked Waters and man is this game fun. It certainly needs a lot of work to become a full blown experience but crewing vehicles in VR will never get old. Steel Heroes - the tank VR game - is coming out this month too! 

Game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/815280/Crooked_Waters/
Game's Discord if you want to test it:
https://discord.gg/M3JtDD
------------------ 
Link to the channel's Twitch, for live shenanigans: 
https://www.twitch.tv/rimmy
Link to the channel's discord, for fun and games:  
https://www.discord.gg/uGXpQ5X
I guess I have a bloody twitter. I hate it. Go away:
https://twitter.com/Rimmy_Downunder
My second channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCknO__IO56Sp73bB_SBto2g
